# R1 Machine Price Calculator Overview

This is a simple HTML application for calculating R1 machine component prices with support for multiple currencies (USD, AUD, CNY).

## Project Structure

- [index.html](mdc:index.html): Main HTML file containing the application UI
- [styles.css](mdc:styles.css): CSS styling for the application 
- [script.js](mdc:script.js): JavaScript code for handling calculations and interactivity
- [README.md](mdc:README.md): Project documentation

## Main Features

- Interactive component price calculator
- Support for multiple currencies (USD, AUD, CNY)
- Dynamic exchange rate adjustments
- Add/remove components functionality
- Automatic calculation of subtotals

